com.acrelec.completesdk

Class Site

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.acrelec.completesdk.Site
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class Site
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Site class defines the destinations of trips. Requires an identifier that uniquely identifies the site. All sites must be preloaded to Complete via the Complete Dashboard.
